Lenne Hardt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lenne_Hardt 0 Lenne Hardt (born May 10) is a voice actress and ring announcer for Japanese mixed martial arts organizations. Her resume includes PRIDE Fighting Championships, DREAM, ONE Championship and Glory World Series and she currently works in Rizin Fighting Federation. She is also the official announcer for Japanese idol group Momoiro Clover Z. Lenne_Hardt ( born May_10 ) is a_voice_actress_and_ring_announcer for Japanese_mixed_martial_arts_organizations .
